# Git Email Privacy Fix

When encountering the `GH007: Your push would publish a private email address` error during a `git push`, or when initializing a new repository, ensure the correct GitHub noreply email is used.

If the error occurs, run the following commands to fix the commit and push:
```bash
git config user.email "22878918+marioisbeck@users.noreply.github.com"
git commit --amend --author="Mario Beck <22878918+marioisbeck@users.noreply.github.com>" --no-edit
git push
```
